// import the library
import React from 'react'
import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'
import { fab } from '@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons'
import { 
    faMagnifyingGlass, 
    faCheck, 
    faArrowLeft, 
    faRightLong, 
    faEye, 
    faHeart, 
    faUser, 
    faForward,
    faUserGroup,
    faPaperPlaneTop
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
library.add(
    fab,
    faMagnifyingGlass, 
    faCheck, 
    faArrowLeft, 
    faRightLong, 
    faEye, 
    faHeart, 
    faUser, 
    faForward,
    faUserGroup,
    faPaperPlaneTop
)
